value:
Tell me...who created this world?
They may be nearer than you think...
Take it from me.

You don't have to be so formal just
because I'm a goddess. Be natural!
Talk to me however feels right.

Desire more. Demand more. It's fine
to live your life with abandon.

Flawed, self-centered, driven by
desire... I find myself drawn to the
foibles of these creatures of flesh.

Can I really have an adventure in
another world? Or am I dreaming
again, inside a galdr of sealing...?

Your friend believes in you. You
must believe in them, too.

On my name, I swear it—the
Goddess's Blessing will come
to everyone.

I continue to change. This makes me
happy.

Defeat and destruction are far
more interesting than stasis.

My power ripples and changes...
Do I have this world to thank for
that?

I am... Freedom. Chaos.
Transformation. Future.
Mystery. I am Yune.

Here I am, far from my own world.
This is not something I anticipated!$k$pBut... No, I'm not bothered... My
curiosity has been ignited. I'm
thoroughly enjoying myself.$k$pThis world is a crucible of chaos...
Just what I like to soak in.$k$pYou hope, take, give, kill, struggle...
Out of all of those needs and desires,
hate and strife are born.$k$pMy other half could never
countenance this. She might just
destroy this beautiful mess one day...$k$pYou—you're my champion. We must
continue fighting for this world!

それっ
きゃああっ！
うそっ！？
Is that all?
How endearing!
So emotional!
Any fight left?
A new transformation...
ふふふっ
I am...freedom. Chaos. Transformation. Future. Mystery. I am Yune.
Oh! You got me! Now it's my turn!
"Dark god"? No, I'm pretty sure I'm not one of those. I am neither holy nor base, neither angel nor devil.
Ashera is neither kind nor loving to the beings of this world.
You should strive to get what you want. Challenge your fate. When all else fails, you can still die fighting.
These creatures are made of some tough meat. Do they even need to hear the divine word?
I have never been alone. There has always been someone else, singing comfort to me.
Why not?
It's your future...
I am mystery.
